body:

The 2022 edition of PyCon DE & PyData Berlin took place 11–13 April 2022 at the bcc Berlin Congress Center. Browse the [archived talks](talks/) and [speakers](speakers/) below, or revisit the [original conference site](https://2022.pycon.de/).
